reviewText: GREAT SELLER, INCREDIBLE PRODUCT, SUPER QUALITY.

I know I can't be objective. Lara is one of my favourite female singers. I only have admired her through her videos and CDs, but, THIS CONCERT IN RUSSIA IS MARVELLOUS. She and Igor make an extraordinary duet. His strong male energy ... Her lovely and beauty female energy ... both make a MUST WATCH concert! Sound is great, filming is great too, it's like being there. I felt I was in the first raw.
